ask<br />\n填下生字咁，所以可以去圖書館借書自己係屋企聽住坐，再計分。做果陣見到唔識嘅生字就記左佢，例如tent等等<br />\n<br />\nspeaking其實我都唔係考得好好，原因係外國人鍾意你直接，一泥就直接答個答案，再解釋；而我兩次都係犯左相同錯誤：加引入段，簡介，例如個鬼佬考官問what do u think about eating turkey is a must in Xmas。我就一開始想簡介xmas係香港係個每個人都好重視嘅節日bilibala...跟住先講我認為係一個must...係簡介果段期間個考官會唔耐煩同埋黑面，所以要單刀直入，佢問乜都好泥第一句就要比答案yes/no/your opinion，唔好咁間接<br />\n<br />\n所以我覺得如果我改到E D我下次應該有7.5-8"},{"pid":"40bbb469f1ae73ed9d62b063da058566da3bae99","tid":1888423,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T20:53:01.000Z","msg":"Carousell大把資源啦 睇到眼殘"},{"pid":"189461767885fce02db91a39613651456553e3bc","tid":1888423,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"Speaking試過一次 6 分 一次 9 分&hellip;<br />\n真係睇你遇到咩人"},{"pid":"40ac4ce16e07bc70e934bbecbe2c15cdb9249488","tid":1888423,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c43ad541cb0b53e47e6206da6c21c1b41a42065","tid":1888423,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40ac4ce16e07bc70e934bbecbe2c15cdb9249488","tid":1888423,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"189461767885fce02db91a39613651456553e3bc","tid":1888423,"uid":48088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T21:00:13.000Z","msg":"Speaking試過一次 6 分 一次 9 分&hellip;<br />\n真係睇你遇到咩人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T02:36:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"下次有機會俾你睇....證書係舊屋"},{"pid":"b158043db87de0f0a78245b2e1f611f853bb0ed3","tid":1888423,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T10:29:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d9a557af9484e36373b8598f19f71c47517f337","tid":1888423,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e503aeec2e6bca3d59638f7c85d2bda3f259ac45","tid":1888423,"uid":19155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c234fa3094723ecda714455711265016bc97540","